  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/078dc0123330a6813f828b04f29eb58a.avif?t=1772598102\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yet Another Climbing Game</strong> is a punishing ascent, a twisted tribute to the agony of determination. You guide your climber with a single, clumsy mechanic, grappling upward with imprecise precision. That’s all there is. With persistence, you might find yourself soaring, stumbling, and sometimes hanging by a thread. Great mysteries and perhaps some reward await those daring (or foolish) enough to reach the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/e1b198d109ce28195ef4ad1c37650f0d.poster.avif?t=1772598102\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/e1b198d109ce28195ef4ad1c37650f0d.webm?t=1772598102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/e1b198d109ce28195ef4ad1c37650f0d.mp4?t=1772598102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To quote the game's inspiration:<br><i>\"Only a person who loves pain will reach the peak, because there is no other way.\" </i>-A random from the internet</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll drag yourself up with a simple but precise control system that seems purpose-built to test your patience. Each grasp, each swing, each slip has the power to make you question your choices. With enough resilience, you might just find your way up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/035830ac277342aa9943fc2afaeb97ae.avif?t=1772598102\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lose your progress, over and over again.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the few who reach the top, something curious awaits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/c14010cd9e19e80bd2979143b61ae791.poster.avif?t=1772598102\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/c14010cd9e19e80bd2979143b61ae791.webm?t=1772598102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/c14010cd9e19e80bd2979143b61ae791.mp4?t=1772598102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/078dc0123330a6813f828b04f29eb58a.avif?t=1772598102\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yet Another Climbing Game</strong> is a punishing ascent, a twisted tribute to the agony of determination. You guide your climber with a single, clumsy mechanic, grappling upward with imprecise precision. That’s all there is. With persistence, you might find yourself soaring, stumbling, and sometimes hanging by a thread. Great mysteries and perhaps some reward await those daring (or foolish) enough to reach the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/e1b198d109ce28195ef4ad1c37650f0d.poster.avif?t=1772598102\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/e1b198d109ce28195ef4ad1c37650f0d.webm?t=1772598102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/e1b198d109ce28195ef4ad1c37650f0d.mp4?t=1772598102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To quote the game's inspiration:<br><i>\"Only a person who loves pain will reach the peak, because there is no other way.\" </i>-A random from the internet</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll drag yourself up with a simple but precise control system that seems purpose-built to test your patience. Each grasp, each swing, each slip has the power to make you question your choices. With enough resilience, you might just find your way up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/035830ac277342aa9943fc2afaeb97ae.avif?t=1772598102\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lose your progress, over and over again.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the few who reach the top, something curious awaits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/c14010cd9e19e80bd2979143b61ae791.poster.avif?t=1772598102\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/c14010cd9e19e80bd2979143b61ae791.webm?t=1772598102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329220/extras/c14010cd9e19e80bd2979143b61ae791.mp4?t=1772598102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
